Ornaments are decorative objects with which Duplicants enjoy sprucing up their colonies. They tend to be smaller than traditional artwork, and possess very high <link=\"DECOR\">Decor</link> value.\n\n<link=\"REQUIREMENTCLASSORNAMENT\">Displayed Ornaments</link> exhibited atop a <link=\"ITEMPEDESTAL\">Pedestal</link> or <link=\"SHELF\">Display Shelf</link> allow a colony to benefit from certain <link=\"ROOMS\">Room</link> bonuses.\n\n